Global Drug of Abuse Saliva Tester Market Insights
Drug of Abuse Saliva Tester Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12% from 2024 to 2030.

Drug of Abuse Saliva Tester Market Overview
The global Drug of Abuse Saliva Tester Market has shown significant growth in recent years, valued at approximately USD 480 million in 2024 and expected to reach USD 750 million by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% during the forecast period. The increasing demand for on-site drug testing in workplaces, schools, and law enforcement agencies, along with a rising awareness of the non-invasive nature of saliva-based drug testing, is expected to drive the market forward. Technological advancements in saliva testing devices and an increasing number of drug testing regulations are also playing key roles in the market expansion.

